### With the VS Code REST Client extension, you can simply click
### "Send Request" to test right from this page.
### 

### heartbeat
GET http://localhost:8080/heartbeat

### create
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/beacons/create_beacon
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "beacon":{
    "id": "2",
    "udi": "00001",
    "type": "BeaconTypeV1.AltBeacon",
    "site_id": "2",
    "label": "TestBeacon2",
    "center": { "type": "Point", "coordinates": [ 0, 0 ] },
    "radius": 50
    }
}

